text: Timoner is a surname found in Spanish-heritage populations and among Ashkenazi Jews (region of Tymanivka, Ukraine). * Chana Timoner (born 1951), Jewish U.S. Army chaplain * Gerard Timoner (born 1958), Filipino priest, head of the Dominicans * Guillermo Timoner (born 1926), Spanish cyclist * Ondi Timoner (born 1972), U.S. film director
title: Timoner
